name: women
description:
Sometimes you have to sit next to him, you do not have to say anything
Just be there and lean on it
Even the strongest women sometimes need support
A safe support that pushes the bottom of their hearts to the value of a woman is much more than these words to leave her alone and pass by her the day you do this, know that you will kill love in a woman's heart
And he will no longer be like you in the past.
